name: Keep a Low Profile, Sect Leader
author: Yuewen Manhua &#40阅文漫画&#41
content: Traveling to the world of Tian Xuan, can’t believe I’ve become a useless sect’s leader!Paying money in the city to be reborn in a game’s realm.Making the players my workers, collecting the main characters from the world as my underlings.If we’re talking about being pretentious, then I’ll only take the number one spot!
